CrossContractDependencies.Description: The contract relies on the presence of an external contract (referred to by `caddress`) that implements a `transferFrom` function to execute the intended transfers.

InterContractConsistencyConditions.Description: The `transfer` function assumes that `caddress` is a valid contract with a `transferFrom` function and that each call to `transferFrom` will execute correctly for each address in `_tos`.
